---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Configuration (RCAN) — OpenCastor Docs"
  description="Understanding the .rcan.yaml configuration file format for OpenCastor robots."
  ogUrl="https://opencastor.com/docs/configuration"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Configuration</p>
    <h1 class="reveal reveal-d1">RCAN YAML Format</h1>
    <p class="reveal reveal-d2">Every OpenCastor robot is defined by a single <code style="padding:2px 6px;font-size:0.8125rem">.rcan.yaml</code> config file following the RCAN specification.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="configuration">
    <div class="code-block reveal" style="margin-bottom: 32px">
      <div class="code-header">
        <div class="code-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span class="code-filename">my_robot.rcan.yaml</span>
      </div>
      <div class="code-body">
<span class="k">rcan_version:</span> <span class="s">"1.6"</span><br><br>
<span class="k">metadata:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">robot_name:</span> <span class="s">"Explorer"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">robot_uuid:</span> <span class="s">"..."</span> <span class="cm"># auto-generated by wizard</span><br><br>
<span class="cm"># --- Agent Block ---</span><br>
<span class="k">agent:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">provider:</span> <span class="s">"anthropic"</span> <span class="cm"># anthropic | google | apple | ollama | ...</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">model:</span> <span class="s">"claude-opus-4-6"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">vision_enabled:</span> <span class="v">true</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">safety_stop:</span> <span class="v">true</span><br><br>
<span class="cm"># --- Tiered Brain Block ---</span><br>
<span class="k">tiered_brain:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">planner:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">provider:</span> <span class="s">"anthropic"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">model:</span> <span class="s">"claude-opus-4-6"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">max_latency_ms:</span> <span class="n">5000</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">fast_brain:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">provider:</span> <span class="s">"huggingface"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">model:</span> <span class="s">"meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">max_latency_ms:</span> <span class="n">500</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">escalation_threshold:</span> <span class="n">0.7</span> <span class="cm"># confidence below this → escalate</span><br><br>
<span class="cm"># --- Camera Block ---</span><br>
<span class="k">camera:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">type:</span> <span class="s">"oakd"</span> <span class="cm"># oakd | csi | usb | hailo | auto</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">depth_enabled:</span> <span class="v">true</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">resolution:</span> <span class="s">"640x480"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">fps:</span> <span class="n">30</span><br><br>
<span class="k">physics:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">type:</span> <span class="s">"differential_drive"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">dof:</span> <span class="n">2</span><br><br>
<span class="k">drivers:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;- <span class="k">protocol:</span> <span class="s">"pca9685_i2c"</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="k">address:</span> <span class="s">"0x40"</span><br>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section reveal">
      <h3>Key Blocks</h3>
      <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li><strong>agent</strong> — Primary AI provider, model, and feature flags.</li>
        <li><strong>tiered_brain</strong> — Multi-tier architecture: planner (slow/smart), fast_brain (fast/cheap).</li>
        <li><strong>reactive</strong> — Hardware-level safety.</li>
        <li><strong>camera</strong> — Camera configuration, sensors, auto-detect flags.</li>
        <li><strong>physics</strong> — Robot kinematics (differential_drive, ackermann, holonomic, arm).</li>
        <li><strong>drivers</strong> — Hardware drivers (PCA9685, Dynamixel, GPIO, serial, HLabs ACB).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top:20px;">
    <a href="/docs/setup-wizard" class="btn btn-secondary">&larr; Setup Wizard</a>
    <a href="/docs/architecture" class="btn btn-secondary">Next: Architecture &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
